('22', '1', '2012-01-18 07:02:03', '2012-01-18 00:02:03', 'I\'ve been neglecting you. But where would I even begin? I\'ve taken a turn towards the taciturn—that definitely seems less funny now that it’s down in writing.  There’s just a friction to communication here. And that’s true of my Thailand writ large: I can’t talk to the other volunteers, I can’t talk to my host family, and I can’t talk to my friends back home. I feel stuck in the same purgatory that I had felt on the plane ride over: I’m not here and I’m not there.', 'Foreign', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'foreign', '', '', '2012-10-26 07:49:35', '2012-10-26 00:49:35', '', '0', 'http://www.weiluen.com/blog/?p=22', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
