('57', '1', '2012-10-21 07:45:28', '2012-10-21 00:45:28', 'Things are starting to turn more normal here. But I\'m not sure what that means. Acclimation is just my euphemism for identity change. But it\'s hard to gauge how much I\'ve changed over here. I\'m marooned from all the comforts of home, all the creature comforts, all of my friends, all of everything that I remember. But you can\'t be backward looking here. You have to befriend the giant lizards that creep around your walls; you have to forget the giant bug swarms that fly into your house; you have to forget about the oppressive heat. It\'s hard. But you have to recognize that you yourself will change far more than you will ever be able to change the place that you live. Every day is a struggle. And it\'s tragic, but there is one place that I recognize my change beyond all else: my ambition. But, perhaps, that\'s just my euphemism for the far more frightening idea that my priorities have changed.\r\n\r\nHere, I\'m reminded of a pithy truth that I seem to have forgotten back home:  self-actualization is awfully hard when you\'re struggling to stay afloat.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/32/water-world_mg_0828_v2\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-55\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-55\" title=\"water-world_mg_0828_v2\" src=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/assets/water-world_mg_0828_v2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"440\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/32/wale-ambition-copy\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-54\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-54\" title=\"wale-ambition-copy\" src=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/assets/wale-ambition-copy-600x600.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Finally A New Layout', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '32-revision-8', '', '', '2012-10-21 07:45:28', '2012-10-21 00:45:28', '', '32', 'http://www.weiluen.com/blog/57', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
