('213', '1', '2012-10-19 07:05:50', '2012-10-19 00:05:50', 'So I touched down in Thailand today. What day is it anyway? I’m definitely not sure. We’re traveling out of Bangkok right now, but Thailand is nothing like what I imagined. I haven’t seen any lasting remnants of flood damage – only modern cars and kitschy lights. I feel that the two Bourdain episodes that I watched back in the States, the grand summation of all my Thailand knowledge, may have, perhaps, created a singular story for my Thailand. Bangkok is posh, even swanky. I guess we’ll see what life looks like 2 hours to the north.', 'Where is Here?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-3', '', '', '2012-10-19 07:05:50', '2012-10-19 00:05:50', '', '19', 'http://www.weiluen.com/blog/213', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
