('228', '1', '2012-10-24 08:02:11', '2012-10-24 01:02:11', 'So I touched down in Thailand today. What day is it anyway? I’m definitely not sure. We’re traveling out of Bangkok right now, but Thailand is nothing like the Thailand of my imagination. I can\'t seem to find any traces of the flood damage that was featured so prominently in my mind\'s eye—only modern cars and kitschy lights. I feel that the two Bourdain episodes that I watched back in the States, the grand summation of my prior knowledge about Thailand, may have, perhaps, created a singular story of Thailand for me. Bangkok is posh, even swanky. But I guess we’ll see what life looks like after driving 2 hours north.', 'Where is Here?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-5', '', '', '2012-10-24 08:02:11', '2012-10-24 01:02:11', '', '19', 'http://www.weiluen.com/blog/228', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
