down the sentence:\n</span></p><p>\n </p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\">  This  is __(name)___. He/She is a/an __(job)__. \n</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\">  He/She is __adjective__.\n</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\">\n								<br/>We can play charades with the individual occupations and job titles mixed with newly learned adjectives. The adjectives will be about descriptions. And it will be about how to describe objects too.  Reintroduce pronoun it. \n</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding-left: 7px; padding-right: 7px; border-top:  none; border-left:  solid black 0.5pt; border-bottom:  solid black 0.5pt; border-right:  solid black 0.5pt\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><strong>III. Practice\n</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><strong>(__55__minutes)\n</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><em>Materials and\n</em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><em>Handouts:\n</em></span></p></td><td style=\"padding-left: 7px; padding-right: 7px; border-top:  none; border-left:  none; border-bottom:  solid black 0.5pt; border-right:  solid black 0.5pt\"><p>\n </p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\">     Teacher asks students to read their worksheet about occupations following the sentence above.<strong>\n								</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><strong>The sentences will be about adjectives in general.\n</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding-left: 7px; padding-right: 7px; border-top:  none; border-left:  solid black 0.5pt; border-bottom:  solid black 0.5pt; border-right:  solid black 0.5pt\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt\"><strong>IV. Application/\n</strong></span></p><p><span st