ly considered using a&nbsp;server-side&nbsp;script for mobile detection—PHP, but I have decided against this method despite its obvious advantage, i.e., older mobile platforms might not be able to process javascript. Many major websites are already utilizing Jquerry mobile as their main platform, so I can see no compelling reason to support legacy platforms.</li>\r\n	<li>I would like to create a custom 404 page.</li>\r\n	<li>I have started to incorporate rich snippet microdata into the main page. This, however, has not been picked up by the Google bots. I am trying to utilize the Schema.org settings, but I seem to have made an error somewhere.</li>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo end on a less technical note, here\'s a quick story about misunderstandings.\r\n\r\nLast week I was eating lunch at one of my schools. My co-teacher gave me a plate to eat off. So after I finished, she asked me if I knew how to wash dishes. Naturally, being too quick to judge, I scoffed at her remark—only in my mind, of course. <em>Who was she to address me with such an imperious tone?</em> I\'m no privileged American brat. I can rough it with the best, right? So—naturally—I shot back with a regrettably brusque \"of course!\" This was the beginning of my downfall. Hindsight is 20/20. I think, my defensiveness in conjunction with an incomplete grasp of Thai turned what was most likely a benign question and/or a genial attempt at assistance into something far uglier than was ever intended. Semiotics are funny like that: two identical signs can somehow signify very disparate meanings.\r\n\r\nI spent the next 20 minutes searching for the dish washing station. And when I found it, hidden among thick bushes, I was greeted with no dish scrubber—just my hands to scrape off the grime.\r\n\r\nWho knew, washing dishes in Thailand isn\'t the same.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/assets/2012-11-19-12.53.31.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-350\" title=\"Washing Dishes\" src=\"http://www.weiluen.com/blog/assets/2012-11-19-12.53.31.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><div style=\"background-image: url(chrome-extension://khpcanbeojalbkpgpmjpdkjnkfcgfkhb/edgebgbot.png); position: static; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 100%; display: block; top: 512px; background-position: 0px 0px;\" id=\"yass_bottom_edge\"></div>', 'Technical Update', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '349-revision-2', '', '', '2012-11-19 17:02:56', '2012-11-19 10:02:56', '', '349', 'http://www.weiluen.com/blog/355', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
